President Uhuru Kenyatta Earlier This Week Fired Agriculture Cabinet Secretary Mwangi Kiunjuri, In A Mini Reshuffles That Also Saw Him Allocate More Money To The Agriculture Docket That Also Received Additional Dockets From The Industrialization Ministry. But Could These Changes Have Been Occasioned By The Pressure On President Uhuru Kenyatta To Silence Noises Within His Mount Kenya Backyard?